1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
