The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
House: gothic-revival, modern
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the doctor is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| House         | gothic-revival          | modern     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 